<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Structure on Marc Bouriot</title><link>https://example.org/series/structure/</link><description>Recent content in Structure on Marc Bouriot</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://example.org/series/structure/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Taxonomies Support</title><link>https://example.org/features/taxonomies-support/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 23:00:00 -0300</pubDate><guid>https://example.org/features/taxonomies-support/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The main taxonomy in the theme is &lt;code&gt;tags&lt;/code&gt;, as it is the one listed under the title in every &amp;ldquo;single&amp;rdquo; page, but it&amp;rsquo;s also possible to set any number of arbitrary taxonomies which will be listed in the side pane details section.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For example, in this site there&amp;rsquo;s the taxonomies &lt;code&gt;topic&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;series&lt;/code&gt; as defined in the config file.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;[&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;taxonomies&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;tag&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;tags&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;topic&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;topics&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;series&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;series&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>